1. Before You Start
You need 3 things installed on your Windows machine before anything else.

Required Software
	â€¢	Node.js v20+ â€” Download from nodejs.org â€” choose the LTS version. This powers Claude Code and your build scripts.
	â€¢	Git â€” Download from git-scm.com. Required for version control and Vercel deployment.
